description.narrative: Component 1: Improved delivery of essential health services in the former states of Upper Nile and Jonglei, which contributes to Child Health, Cross-Sectoral Communication For Development, Immunization, Maternal And Newborn Health, Operations Support To Programme Delivery. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Children under five years and pregnant women use more equitable and better quality essential maternal, newborn and child health services
